review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: First of all clinic is very clean and have a creative interior, so many up to date medical equipments are used here. very best environment for a world class treatment.my friend referred me to Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing aid Clinica and when I met Dr.Vesta ,she is very friendly and  caring .Other doctors simply treat their patients with medicines but forget to do the most important thing which she does – help them to move on with their lives with motivating words and inspirational thoughts. Thanks for everything doc.

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: Hey guys! This is Anand here. I've consulted Dr. Vesta for tooth fracture. Since from the day one she's has been very nice in handling patient and explains the issue in a simple manner  which a layman can also understand. She answers to all your problems and doubts without any hesitation. I've started RCT and gonna fix dental crown in upcoming sitting. I thought I can drop in a review after the procedure is over. I trust them and it made me to write now itself. Anyways I'll update my review after few weeks. If your objective is care and best treatment then you can blindly visit them for sure.True vfm. Thanks Dr. Vesta and team.

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: I was worried that I will have severe sensitivity while cleaning my tooth. But when Dr. Vesta did cleaning she  gently cleaned the tooth and she made sure that I have no discomfort while doing the procedure. She took one hour to clean the tooth. She was not worried about spending time with me. But she was more concerned only about my senstiviy issue. Highly recommended. Unlike other doctors she doesn't push the work if some one else walks in without an appt. Pl make sure u confirm the appt before u reach the clinic.

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: I had a broken discolored front tooth. The dentist whom I visited told me there is no option fr treating the tooth other than extraction.He advised extraction followed by implants which was very expensive. I was worried about it.I thought of getting an second opinion and I found Dr.Vesta samuel from Facebook. I visited her . she cooly said there is no need to extract the tooth. I was surprised. Then she did a post and core and gave me crown which looks very natural. I am very happy and great full to her . Thank you doc. I would recommend this doctor for dental treatments in a better and less stressfull way.

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text:
For me dentist and dental chair means pain. The very thought of dentist scares me . That's y perhaps I was ignoring going to a dentist. After hearing abt Dr.Vesta from the internet, I had the courage to go meet her. I underwent 2 root canals. It was like a cake walk,compared to the root canal that I did with a mother dentist.There was no pain during the treatment.
The way she injected anaesthesia was excellent, I just felt the liquid going in.Earlier dentist use to give anaesthesia which is very painful. I truly admire her soft medical skills. Highly recommended fr painless dentistry.

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: Dr.Vesta is very good. On the top the clinic is excellent in terms of facilities and technology.I had a painless root canal from this clinic.I would say this is the best place for root canal treatment.There was no hurry for the other patients.She focused on what is beneficial for me rather than doing a root canal and taking some money for it,which is a trend in dentist doctors(corporates,multi speciality dental centres) Really thankful to Dr.Vesta. Its worth walking into stunning smiles clinic for a stunning smile.Would recommend her as a family dentist.

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: Dr. Vesta is a person who still treats patients with utmost love and care , keeping in mind that being a doc is a noble profession. She handled my tooth so well took time to understand history and then suggested the best and cost effective way to addresd it!! Kudos and continue the good work !!

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: I had been suffering from severe tooth pain caused by decay for almost a week. I had consulted Dr Lydia for tooth decay pain, she insisted to take a X-ray, then examined and suggested for root canal treatment as the infection was severe. It's a simple procedure she performed by first cleaning the infected area and  filling it with rubber like substance. The pain was quite bearable and she also saved my precious tooth from removal. My heartfelt thanks for her kind and positive approach.

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: I found Dr. Vesta on a google search and I wasn’t disappointed at all, so much so that I even brought my children for their root canal and crown treatment. She was very thorough and meticulous in her approach, taking her time explaining every little detail about the issues, which put us at ease. She was easily available on call outside of the appointments as well. Over all I had a very good experience with her as my dentist. 10/10 for her friendly demeanor, service and treatment.

review.practice_name: Stunning Smiles Dental & Hearing Aid Clinic

survey_response.review_text: The doctor provides total importance for hygiene. Most important factor is the doctor is not in a hurry. She spends time with the patients and takes care of them with total affection and care needed for senior citizens like my wife. Dr. Praveena, Dental surgeon is well trained to take care with least pain. I recommend the doctor for all senior citizens.
